            "notes": "The deck focuses on ramping up mana quickly to play big threats and combo pieces. It utilizes cards like Azusa, Exploration, and Summer Bloom to play multiple lands per turn, allowing for explosive starts. It also includes tutors like Expedition Map, Sylvan Scrying, and Worldly Tutor to find key pieces like Dark Depths and Thespian's Stage for the powerful combo. The deck has ways to protect its key pieces with cards like Sylvan Safekeeper and Song of the Dryads. Additionally, it can generate card advantage with cards like Greater Good and Sylvan Library. Overall, the deck aims to overwhelm opponents with big creatures and powerful combos while controlling the board with its mana advantage."
